The Film Lions celebrate creativity of the moving image. Entries needed to demonstrate brilliant brand storytelling intended for a screen through filmed content created for TV, cinema, online and out-of-home experiences. #CannesLions2017: Film shortlistThe Cannes Lions Film shortlist has been released, with work from SA making the cut...1 day ago A total of 85 Film Lions were awarded from the shortlist of 271. The Grand Prix went to OMD UK, 4Creative and Channel 4 London for Channel 4 Paralympics' jazzy, upbeat We're the Superheroes,' which also won a Gold Integrated Lion on the night. Find out more about Canadian drummer Alvin Law, a thalidomide survivor who can do more with his lower limbs than most do with their hands - he also plays the piano and trombone with his feet - in the video interview below: Ogilvy Joburg also added to its haul with a Gold Lion for Cadbury Bubbly 'Pre-Joy', with production by Bomb Films, sound and composition by Howard Music, post-production work by Ministry of Illusion and media by Starcom Worldwide: See the full table of winners below. Film Lions Winners EntrantTitleClientProductAwardBLINK PRODUCTIONS, London / 4CREATIVE, LondonWE'RE THE SUPERHUMANSCHANNEL 4PARALYMPICSGrand Prix PUBLICIS ITALY, MilanJACKIEHEINEKENBEERGold LionWIEDEN+KENNEDY, Portland5 YEAR PLANOLD SPICETOILETRIESGold LionWIEDEN+KENNEDY, DelhiDA DA DINGNIKE DELHICLOTHING, FOOTWEAR AND ACCESSORIESGold LionWIEDEN+KENNEDY AMSTERDAMWHAT ARE GIRLS MADE OF?NIKENIKEGold LionWIEDEN+KENNEDY, PortlandUNLIMITED COURAGENIKECLOTHING / FOOTWEAR / ACCESSORIESGold Lion CampaignWIEDEN+KENNEDY, PortlandUNLIMITED YOUTHNIKECLOTHING / FOOTWEAR / ACCESSORIESGold Lion CampaignWIEDEN+KENNEDY, PortlandUNLIMITED WILLNIKECLOTHING / FOOTWEAR / ACCESSORIESGold Lion CampaignDROGA5, New YorkTHE TRUTH IS HARD TO FIND: HICKSTHE NEW YORK TIMESNEWS SUBSCRIPTIONGold Lion CampaignDROGA5, New YorkTHE TRUTH IS HARD TO FIND: DENTONTHE NEW YORK TIMESNEWS SUBSCRIPTIONGold Lion CampaignTBWA\PARISHALLOWEEN - TVB